{"tid":1747271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上熱門] 你地而家係咪想幫禮義廉贏呀？","createTime":"2019-11-23T06:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T07:46:11.000Z","uid":69787,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fc49d18663897b46c0b60a16c06a10dd46ce9b5e","tid":1747271,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"而家全世界既風都係吹緊要朝早投票因爲有機會close票站<br />\n啱<br />\n但諗深一層全世界都知 代表對家都知<br />\n而以往選舉策略不嬲都係越遲投越好<br />\n因為對家越難即刻動員到老人院資源去配票<br />\n我哋而家個個都朝早湧晒去投票 其實咪即係益左對家容易啲掌握到票向 然後容易啲配票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真我哋朝早去投票 佢哋咪安排老人院車啲呀婆呀伯下午去投囉<br />\n佢哋冇損失之餘仲會令到我地更加易輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但朝早投票又已經放哂風好難扭轉啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以！我動議：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港票站和你排</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使我地大部份人朝早投票，都唔好咁天真嬌咁諗住快快脆脆投完就算，而應該要和你塞票站，增加對家投票成本，就算老人院啲阿婆呀伯嚟到都仲未投到票!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">排到，係門口企一企，諗一諗，哎，心情唔好唔投啦，返去換套衫再排過。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n排隊個陣玩電話，唔係好覺前面條友已經行左，行到差唔多頭，咦，十年冇聯絡既朋友黎搵我喎，打個電話先。喂，聽電話呢啲，咁私隱既野，前後左右聽到曬點得，梗係離隊聽，咁離左隊，當然要重新排過，行翻隊尾再嚟多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\npopo周？癡線，家陣排隊投票都唔俾？<br />\n淨係帶電話，身分證同封信佢吹得我脹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n然後有部份人可以standby唔好朝早咁快投住(當然佢哋朝早都可以去慢慢諗下投唔投啦 唔俾人諗嫁？) <br />\n之前咪有人建議可以全日有人輪流係票站幫手點算 <br />\n邊個時間少咗好多後生但係好多阿婆阿伯嚟排隊 <br />\n嗰班standby既人就即刻落黎同各位老人家一齊排隊一齊投！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n其實都諗咗好耐講唔講<br />\n怕俾人話想帶風向<br />\n只係禮義廉咁撚賤格<br />\n大家brainstorm下有多個方向都未嘗唔好<br />\n有bug歡迎下面屌鳩我<br />\n最怕真係無人講然後中左禮義廉伏<br />\n<br />\n血債一定唔可以票償<br />\n但係制度内外都要抗爭<br />\n我哋可以做嘅都要盡做<br />\n聽日唔撚可以輸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.s建議排隊塞時真係喬裝中年人，純粹玩下電話或者未諗清楚投邊個，唔好搞事，費事又比藉口對家話我地阻人投票，屌你老母諗諗吓唔記得咗想投邊個想諗清楚姐，唔撚得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911f7811f91547cf9f6d7d796991a89aec0c926d","tid":1747271,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"17eaf7135ba6e4c69111e6227e6c8cf1fde82c20","tid":1747271,"uid":295124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:00:19.000Z","msg":"配票係比例代表制WOR....."},{"pid":"ccdc457748bd9173231fbf4581beee34b7acb174","tid":1747271,"uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n區議會配你老母<br />\n老人院係唔係都出動架啦"},{"pid":"05d728707c2e4ef7a888286905ec328604c49d94","tid":1747271,"uid":31548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"老友 幫你推"},{"pid":"7c4864fd324328dfec5908c7f0cb3d0a1d2ba24c","tid":1747271,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"我想人權法制裁埋班泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea544f5d2e21e3547fc362e13a118bdb0eb78a5c","tid":1747271,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"如果下午閂左票站咁點？"},{"pid":"dd93c52b6f88dad88f9922c35124ff3522d22fce","tid":1747271,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZfvUR1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZfvUR1.jpg&h=f66cb420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f306278563987d51bc1edb364175a33d4e312677","tid":1747271,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746369</a>"},{"pid":"097f2cac1b80724aef5f01498e22cea8bed2a1ea","tid":1747271,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"屌我發現好多人誤會左焦土/攬炒嘅意思<br />\n<br />\n焦土/攬炒係要你同對手同歸於盡呀，唔係自己消滅自己呀，係自己死都要攬埋你班仆街建制狗死呀<br />\n<br />\n所以唔投票唔係攬炒，而係自己殺死自己/俾建制狗騎劫民意「止暴制亂」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fe7a286c102660f04fc90fdf3483c25432d981","tid":1747271,"uid":251265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"企圖抹黑民主派，呼籲手足投白票一律視為共諜"},{"pid":"23acf5ee17c2f451aed4853b0d7aa6302683a38c","tid":1747271,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea544f5d2e21e3547fc362e13a118bdb0eb78a5c","tid":1747271,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"如果下午閂左票站咁點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"最好就大家朝早落去Standby<br />\n如果見到一車一車老人家已經黎晒就貫徹本身個計劃照朝早盡投<br />\n但冇理由咁戇鳩如果個票站冇乜老人家都自己走去投晒揭曬底牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1b3ea1db9f42a6270cce23f5e8912510cea557","tid":1747271,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"097f2cac1b80724aef5f01498e22cea8bed2a1ea","tid":1747271,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"屌我發現好多人誤會左焦土/攬炒嘅意思<br />\n<br />\n焦土/攬炒係要你同對手同歸於盡呀，唔係自己消滅自己呀，係自己死都要攬埋你班仆街建制狗死呀<br />\n<br />\n所以唔投票唔係攬炒，而係自己殺死自己/俾建制狗騎劫民意「止暴制亂」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"點都要投票!<br />\n制度內都要抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f99410c3aadf899c98e4e85502d7837b3fff69d","tid":1747271,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"同埋發現好多人好傻豬豬咁諗住投完就走<br />\n萬一佢下午其實唔close票站<br />\n啲阿婆阿伯下午嚟到暢通無阻咁投票咪仆街<br />\n點都要啲老人院阿婆阿伯企耐啲慢慢排隊然後頂唔撚順等到走啦"},{"pid":"c0bc3485ea6f51e5c8e98bb16ac05555f225ca98","tid":1747271,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致 撞區候選人，<br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>申請不反通知書，否則只有零票。</span></span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=72400a34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a>"},{"pid":"2f994bd5e1992eeff1739aa3238f0276c4c82131","tid":1747271,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6643cc3da8e56dd21c18f8c0c30e8b648b27f09","tid":1747271,"uid":296583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1518c751765905d6ae58dfdb1484e36d9531f531","tid":1747271,"uid":10605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"認同 建制不嬲都係朝早問卷估方向<br />\n晏晝立即搵旅遊巴去老人院<br />\n以前不嬲都係盡量遲少少投票<br />\n當然唔好咁過分臨閂門之前嗰幾個字<br />\n都唔明點解今年個風向係叫啲人朝早投票<br />\n朝早已經揭晒底牌 唔知做咩9"}]}